short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: gRPC-Gateway Developer Tools for debugging applications' network requests to a gRPC-Gateway backend

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds a "grpc" network tab that can be used to inspect the data payloads in your applications' gRPC requests.
